Mockup Description for Command Center (Version 2 - Improved Layout)

Improved layout of the Command Center dashboard.

Changes:
- Modular grid layout for better responsiveness
- Added sidebar for quick actions
- Better spacing and alignment

Layout:
- Left sidebar: Quick sync status and alerts
- Center: KPI dashboard with charts
- Right: Recent activities and AI insights

Hierarchy:
- Primary: KPI charts
- Secondary: Sidebar and activities

Usability:
- Improved navigation with tabs, enhanced buttons